02:27.169 --> 02:29.569
{y:i} And the jungle fire was burning

02:29.769 --> 02:32.170
{y:i} Down the track came a hobo hikin'

02:32.270 --> 02:34.771
{y:i} And he said, boys, I'm not turning

02:34.771 --> 02:37.571
{y:i} I'm headed for a land
{y:i} that's far away

02:37.671 --> 02:39.972
{y:i} Beside the crystal fountains

02:40.072 --> 02:44.973
{y:i} So come with me, we'll go and see
{y:i} the big rock candy mountains

02:44.973 --> 02:47.473
{y:i} In the big rock candy mountains

02:47.674 --> 02:50.074
{y:i} There's a land
{y:i} that's fair and bright

02:50.174 --> 02:52.375
