45:03.248 --> 45:05.349
We ain't got time for shenanigans!

45:05.549 --> 45:07.649
Sweet Jesus, Everett.

45:07.849 --> 45:11.650
They left his heart!

45:33.255 --> 45:35.956
Delmar, what the heck's got into you?

45:36.056 --> 45:37.556
Can't you see it, Everett?

45:37.756 --> 45:41.157
Them sirens did this to Pete.

45:41.157 --> 45:46.958
They loved him up and turned
him into a... horny toad.

45:50.759 --> 45:52.159
Pete!

45:52.460 --> 45:54.760
Pete! Pete!

45:54.960 --> 45:58.561
Pete! Pete!

45:58.561 --> 46:03.362
Pete! Pete!

46:08.963 --> 46:13.364
