46:13.464 --> 46:16.765
It's me... Delmar.

46:16.865 --> 46:20.166
- Everett.
- Delmar, what the...?!

46:20.366 --> 46:23.767
What are we gonna do?!

46:32.269 --> 46:33.869
I'm not sure that's Pete.

46:34.069 --> 46:37.270
