fine restaurant like this one.

46:53.974 --> 46:55.574
The good folks'd go off their feed.

46:55.774 --> 46:59.475
Hey. I just don't think it's right
keeping him under wraps,

46:59.475 --> 47:01.075
like we was ashamed of him.

47:01.275 --> 47:03.376
If it is Pete, I am ashamed of him.

47:03.476 --> 47:07.477
The way I see it, he got what he deserved.
Fornicatin' with some whore of Babylon.

47:07.677 --> 47:09.977
These things don't happen
for no reason, Delmar.

47:10.077 --> 47:11.978
It's obviously a judgment
on Pete's character.

47:12.278 --> 47:16.779
Well, the two of us was fixin' to fornicate.

47:16.879 --> 47:19.579
You're going to have to excuse
my rusticated friend,

47:19.579 --> 47:22.780
unaccustomed as he is
to city manners and all.

47:22.880 --> 47:23.880
Hmm?

47:24.080 --> 47:27.081
I guess we'll have ourselves
a couple of steaks

47:27.281 --> 47:29.282
and some, uh, gratinated potatoes,

47:29.382 --> 47:31.982
and wash it down with
your finest bubbly wine.

47:32.182 --> 47:36.483
Oh, I don't suppose you have any
nits or grubs back in the pantry?

47:36.483 --> 47:38.984
Maybe the chef could prepare...

47:39.184 --> 47:42.685
No, just bring us a couple
of leaves of raw cabbage.

47:42.785 --> 47:44.585
- Yes, sir.
- Thank you.

47:44.685 --> 47:48.886
I don't believe I've seen you boys around
here before. Allow me to introduce myself.

47:48.986 --> 47:52.887
Name of Daniel Teague, known Known in
these precincts as Big Dan Teague,

47:52.987 --> 47:55.688
Or, pressed for time, Big Dan!
Tout court!

47:55.888 --> 48:00.289
How you doing, Big Dan? My name's Ulysses Everett
McGill. This is my associate, Delmar O'Donnel.

48:00.289 --> 48:03.989
I detect, like me, you're
endowed with the gift of gab.

48:03.989 --> 48:07.890
I flatter myself that such is the case.
In my line of work, it's plum necessary.

48:08.090 --> 48:11.391
The one thing you don't want

48:11.491 --> 48:13.892
is air in the conversation.

48:14.092 --> 48:17.292
Once again, we find ourselves in agreement.
What kind of work do you do, Big Dan?

48:17.392 --> 48:19.793
Sales, Mr. McGill, sales!
And what do I sell?

48:19.993 --> 48:21.893
The truth. Every blessed word of it.

48:22.093 --> 48:24.094
From Genesis on down to Revelations.

48:24.294 --> 48:26.895
That's right, the word of God,
which, let me tell you,

48:27.095 --> 48:30.895
there's damn good money in
during these times of woe and want.

48:30.996 --> 48:35.096
People are looking for answers, and Big Dan
sells the only book that's got 'em.

48:35.196 --> 48:39.798
And what do you do, you and
your, uh, tongue-tied friend?

48:39.898 --> 48:41.998
We, uh...

48:42.098 --> 48:43.698
We're adventurers, sir,

48:43.898 --> 48:45.499
currently pursuing a certain opportunity,

48:45.799 --> 48:47.699
but we're open to others as well.

48:47.899 --> 48:50.900
I like your style, young man. So
I'm going to propose you a proposition.

48:50.900 --> 48:55.501
You cover my bill so I won't have to go back upstairs,
get your waitress to wrap your dinner picnic-style

48:55.601 --> 48:58.102
and we shall retire to more private environs,

48:58.202 --> 49:00.802
where I'll tell you of the vast amounts of money

49:01.002 --> 49:02.903
in the service of God Almighty.

49:03.003 --> 49:06.804
Well, why not? If nothing else, I could
use some civilised conversation.

49:06.904 --> 49:09.204
Don't forget your shoe box, friend.

49:09.304 --> 49:12.605
Damn shame!
Goddam campaign is lagging!

49:12.705 --> 49:17.106
We need a shot in the arm. You
hear me, boys? In the goddam arm!

49:17.206 --> 49:21.507
If the election was held tomorrow, that
sumbitch Stokes would win in a walk!

49:21.607 --> 49:24.408
He's the reform candidate, Daddy.

49:24.508 --> 49:27.308
- Yeah?
- People like that reform.

49:27.408 --> 49:29.609
Maybe we should get us some.

49:29.709 --> 49:32.910
I'll reform you, you
soft-headed son of a bitch.

49:33.110 --> 49:35.810
How we gonna run reform
when we're the damn incumbent?!

49:35.810 --> 49:38.911
Is that the best idea you boys
can come up with? Reform?!

49:39.011 --> 49:41.512
Weepin' Jesus on the cross.

49:41.712 --> 49:43.212
That's it!

49:43.312 --> 49:46.013
You may as well start drafting my
concession speech right now.

49:46.213 --> 49:47.713
OK, Pappy.

49:47.813 --> 49:50.313
I'm just making a point,
you stupid son'bitch.

49:50.514 --> 49:53.814
- Give me back that hat! Harry up!
- Pappy's just makin' a point.

49:54.014 --> 49:56.515
Shut up!

50:10.618 --> 50:14.619
Thank you boys for that fricassee.
I'm a man of large appetites.

50:14.719 --> 50:17.720
Even with lunch under my belt,
I was feelin' a mite peckish.

50:17.720 --> 50:18.820
It's our pleasure, Big Dan.

50:19.020 --> 50:22.321
Thank you, as well, for
the conversational hiatus.

50:22.421 --> 50:25.421
I generally refrain from
speech during gustation.

50:25.521 --> 50:28.522
There are those who attempt
both at the same time.

50:28.722 --> 50:30.623
I find it coarse and vulgar.

50:30.723 --> 50:33.823
- Where were we?
- Making money in the Lord's service.

50:34.023 --> 50:37.424
You don't say much friend, but when you do,
it's to the point and I salute you for it.

50:37.524 --> 50:39.325
Yes, Bible sales.

50:39.425 --> 50:43.726
Now, the trade is not a complicated one.
There are but two things to learn.

50:43.726 --> 50:45.326
One: being able to find a wholesaler,

50:45.626 --> 50:47.126
The word of God in bulk, as it were.

50:47.326 --> 50:51.327
Two: how to recognise your customer.
Who are you dealing with?

50:51.327 --> 50:54.328
It's an exercise in psychology, so to speak.

50:54.428 --> 51:02.030
And it is that which I propose
to give you a lesson in right now.

51:02.030 --> 51:05.631
I like to think I'm a pretty astute
student of the human scene too, Big Dan.

51:05.631 --> 51:08.931
No doubt, brother. I figured
as much back at the restaurant.

51:09.031 --> 51:14.233
That's why I invited you all out here
for this advanced tutorial.

51:14.233 --> 51:16.733
What's going on, Big Dan?

51:16.933 --> 51:19.934
It's all about the money, boys!
That's the answer!

51:20.034 --> 51:24.735
Gol... durned... money!

51:24.835 --> 51:25.735
I don't get it, Big Dan.

51:25.835 --> 51:28.936
Raah!

51:28.836 --> 51:32.437
Now, I'll just take your show cards.

51:32.637 --> 51:37.138
Yaah!

51:40.538 --> 51:44.139
And whatever you got in the hole.

51:47.040 --> 51:51.441
What the... there ain't
nothin' but a damn toad.

51:51.541 --> 51:57.442
No, you don't understand.
That's Pete.

51:59.643 --> 52:01.143
Pete.

52:01.243 --> 52:05.144
You know these things give you warts?

52:12.146 --> 52:13.546
End of lesson.

52:16.047 --> 52:18.447
So long, boys. Hee hee hee!

52:18.547 --> 52:20.748
See you in the funny papers.

52:20.948 --> 52:25.149
Y'all seen the end of Big Dan Teague.

52:45.853 --> 52:51.154
Where are they? Talk, you
unreconstructed whelp of a whore!

52:51.154 --> 52:53.055
Where they headed?

52:53.255 --> 52:56.456
- Aah!
- Your screams ain't gonna save your flesh.

52:56.656 --> 52:59.156
- Aah!
- Only your tongue is, boy.

52:59.256 --> 53:01.857
- Where they headed?
- Aah!

53:13.260 --> 53:16.660
Whoa, hound.

53:22.562 --> 53:26.162
Sweet summer rain.

53:27.663 --> 53:31.064
Like God's own mercy.

53:31.164 --> 53:34.064
Your two friends
have abandoned you, Pete.

53:34.264 --> 53:37.465
They don't seem to care about your hide.

53:42.166 --> 53:45.367
OK.

53:48.968 --> 53:52.468
Stairway to heaven, Pete.

53:54.369 --> 53:55.969
We shall all meet by and by.

53:56.169 --> 53:58.770
God damn it!

54:00.670 --> 54:02.271
God forgive me!

54:02.471 --> 54:05.571
Hold.

54:15.274 --> 54:18.974
Believe me, Delmar, he would
have wanted us to press on.

54:19.174 --> 54:23.175
Pete, rest his soul,
was one sour-ass son of a bitch

54:23.275 --> 54:26.376
and not given to acts
of pointless sentimentality.

54:26.376 --> 54:29.377
It just don't seem right, diggin'
up that treasure without him.

54:29.577 --> 54:32.678
Maybe it was for the best
that he was squished.

54:32.778 --> 54:36.178
Why, he... was barely
a sentient being and.

54:36.178 --> 54:39.479
As soon as we get ourselves cleaned up,
get a little smell'um in our hair,

54:39.679 --> 54:42.480
