state of Mississippi

56:16.501 --> 56:20.402
cannot afford four more years
of Pappy O'Daniel!

56:20.502 --> 56:23.303
Four more years of cronyism!

56:23.403 --> 56:26.303
Nepotism! Rascalism!

56:26.303 --> 56:30.104
Of service to the interests!

56:30.304 --> 56:33.405
Now, the choice, she's a clear.

56:33.505 --> 56:37.006
Pappy O'Daniel, slave of the interests.

56:37.206 --> 56:41.407
Homer Stokes, servant of the
little man. Right, little fella?

56:41.507 --> 56:42.707
He ain't lyin'!

56:42.907 --> 56:46.808
And ladies and gentlemen,
the little man has admonished me

56:46.808 --> 56:49.208
to grasp the broom of reform

56:49.409 --> 56:51.909
and sweep this state clean!

56:52.109 --> 56:55.210
It's gonna be,
"Back to the flour mill, Pappy"!

56:55.310 --> 56:57.710
The interests can take care of themselves!

56:57.810 --> 57:01.711
Come Tuesday, we're gonna
sweep the rascals out!

57:03.512 --> 57:07.413
Clean government is yours for the asking!

57:09.413 --> 57:12.214
Folks, now the little Wharvey gals!

57:13.714 --> 57:17.815
