01:11:37.110 --> 01:11:39.810
{y:i} Whoa, death, someone would pray

01:11:39.910 --> 01:11:44.712
{y:i} Could you wait to call me
{y:i} another day?

01:11:44.812 --> 01:11:45.812
{y:i} Children pray...

01:11:46.012 --> 01:11:50.513
That's Tommy.
